=== Group Provider ===

==== Functionality ====

Creates a [[Admin:ResourceGroups | resource group]] based on the results of a SPARQL query.

{{#widget: com.fluidops.iwb.widget.DisplayConfigurationWidget
| clazz = com.fluidops.iwb.provider.GroupProvider
| type = 'DESCRIPTION'
}}
Go back to [[Help:Providers | Providers ]]

==== Configuration Settings ====
{{#widget: com.fluidops.iwb.widget.DisplayConfigurationWidget
| clazz = com.fluidops.iwb.provider.GroupProvider
}}

==== Example ====

Let's assume the following query lists all items that Joe is responsible for:
''<nowiki>select ?item where :joe :responsible ?item</nowiki>''.
The group provider :JoesItems is defined and run using this query.
This makes :JoesItems a Platform:ResourceGroup and associates all items with the group.
